## 3. Architectural Taxonomy

### 3.1 Early Fusion

Early fusion architectures concatenate visual tokens with text tokens at the input layer. The visual tokens are produced by a frozen or fine-tuned vision encoder $$f_v$$, projected into the LLM's embedding space via a learned projection matrix $$W_p$$:

$$z_v = W_p \cdot f_v(I) \in \mathbb{R}^{N_v \times d}$$ {math: latex}

The combined input sequence becomes:

$$X = [z_v; z_t] \in \mathbb{R}^{(N_v + N_t) \times d}$$ {math: latex}

**Advantages:**
- Simple architecture; minimal additional parameters
- Full bidirectional attention between modalities
- Easy to scale with larger LLM backbones

**Disadvantages:**
- Quadratic attention cost with image token count
- Fixed visual token budget (typically 256–576 tokens)
- No modality-specific processing

### 3.2 Cross-Attention Fusion

||| table id="t-crossattn" caption="Table 3: Cross-Attention Architectures"
| Model          | LLM Backbone   | Vision Encoder | Cross-Attn Layers | Total Params | MMLU  | MMBench |
|----------------|----------------|----------------|--------------------|--------------|-------|---------|
| Flamingo-80B   | Chinchilla-70B | NFNet-F6       | Every 4th          | 80B          | 71.2  | 68.4    |
| IDEFICS2-8B    | Mistral-7B     | SigLIP-SO400M  | Every 2nd          | 8.4B         | 63.8  | 72.1    |
| Qwen-VL-Max    | Qwen2-72B     | ViT-bigG       | Adaptive           | 72B+         | 82.4  | 83.2    |
| InternVL2-76B  | InternLM2-Chat | InternViT-6B   | Every layer        | 76B          | 80.1  | 81.5    |
| Cambrian-34B   | Yi-34B        | Ensemble (4)    | Selective          | 34B          | 75.6  | 79.8    |
|||

### 3.3 Mixture-of-Experts (MoE) Architectures

The MoE approach routes different modalities (or sub-problems) to specialized expert networks:

$$y = \sum_{i=1}^{N} g_i(x) \cdot E_i(x)$$ {math: latex}

where $$g_i(x)$$ {math: latex} is the gating function and $$E_i(x)$$ {math: latex} is the $$i$$-th expert.

||| table id="t-moe" caption="Table 4: MoE Multimodal Models"
| Model              | Total Params | Active Params | Experts | Modality Routing | MMLU  |
|--------------------|--------------|---------------|---------|------------------|-------|
| Mixtral-Vision     | 46.7B        | 12.9B         | 8       | Shared           | 74.2  |
| DeepSeek-VL2       | 236B         | 28B           | 64      | Modality-aware   | 83.1  |
| Grok-Vision        | 314B         | 86B           | 8       | Shared           | 85.2  |
| MoE-LLaVA-3x7B    | 21B          | 7B            | 3       | Learned          | 68.5  |
|||

