### 4.2 Scaling Laws

We observe a consistent log-linear relationship between model parameters and average benchmark performance:

$$\text{Avg Score} \approx 12.3 \cdot \log_2(\text{Active Params in B}) + 45.7$$ {math: latex}

with $$R^2 = 0.89$$ {math: latex} across all 127 models.

