| Claude 3.5 Sonnet | 3.00                   | 82.9      | 27.6             |
| Qwen-VL-Max       | 1.20                   | 81.2      | 67.7             |
| Phi-4-Vision-14B  | 0.15 (self-hosted)     | 76.7      | 511.3            |
